         url('${resourcesFolderName}/animeace-webfont.woff2') format('woff2'),

         url('${resourcesFolderName}/animeace-webfont.ttf') format('truetype'),

    font-weight: normal;

}

</style>

<style>
@font-face {
    font-family: 'zelda_dx_tt_brkregular';
    src: url('${resourcesFolderName}/zeldadxt-webfont.eot');
    src: url('${resourcesFolderName}/zeldadxt-webfont.eot?#iefix') format('embedded-opentype'),
         url('${resourcesFolderName}/zeldadxt-webfont.woff2') format('woff2'),
         url('${resourcesFolderName}/zeldadxt-webfont.woff') format('woff'),
         url('${resourcesFolderName}/zeldadxt-webfont.ttf') format('truetype'),
         url('${resourcesFolderName}/zeldadxt-webfont.svg#zelda_dx_tt_brkregular') format('svg');
    font-weight: normal;
    font-style: normal;

}
</style>

<style>
	
		body{
			
			/*image pixelation*/
			image-rendering: pixelated;
			image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges;
			image-rendering: crisp-edges;

		
			background-image: url("${resourcesFolderName}/IMG_STARS1.gif");
  			background-repeat: repeat;
		}
		
		padding around the hype container
		#index_hype_container{

			/*top: 2%;*/
		
			min-width: 640px;
			min-height: 960px;
		}
		
		/*SITE PAGE inspection messages*/
		.inspectionMessage{
			display: inline;
  			background: white !important;
  			box-shadow: 10px 10px 0px black;
  			/*transform: rotate(-4.5deg) !important;*/
  			cursor: url("${resourcesFolderName}/CURSOR.png"), auto !important;
		}
		
		/*items obtained screen (zelda like)*/
		.itemObtainedMessage{
			display: inline;
  			background: black !important;
  			box-shadow: 10px 10px 0px black;
		}
		
		/*any changes to the verm (like brightness)*/
		.verm{
			transition: all 1s ease;
		}
		
		/*objects in the background that will be set to 0 transparency when you "win" -- chaos should fade out*/
		.destruction{
			transition: all 3s ease;
		}
	
	</style>
Help us! The vermin is eating our village!
